{"tid":1309623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"識玩梗係唔止罷食吉野家","createTime":"2019-07-12T09:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:29:53.000Z","uid":279063,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"26a8a501cdf3750e14f974de530e74219c78c866","tid":1309623,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"要令到佢本身啲客都無埋<br />\n連啲員工都唔想喺佢度做嘢<br />\n最有效嘅方法係<strong>將佢地嘅分店政治化</strong><br />\n可以試下喺店內整連儂牆，或者舉牌撐警<br />\n令到任何人一諗起「吉野家」就即刻聯想到「可能會有衝突」<br />\n不論政見，連經過吉野家分店都會擔心自己安全，連入都唔敢入<br />\n咁先係做到嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申P牌多多指教"},{"pid":"4b771a5c80a317e51b666e95ed59f742728e8c09","tid":1309623,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"[正撚量] 到底有冇暴動呀屌？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309462</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a439580bdb7e5cec1c0b116179ab3bcb2c69f59","tid":1309623,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"42964b781710937b2397c7594ceacf42624ac1c3","tid":1309623,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:54:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78896aa2d5e64562ba14b7bf1e5c2c46afc03674","tid":1309623,"uid":144492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"我建議有人喺間舖度嘔<br />\n嘔唔犯法㗎嘛<br />\n間間都有人嘔 <br />\n一見人嘔 其他人都反胃"},{"pid":"d0057cae2238383b47c7b4cb19262e7e6ab89763","tid":1309623,"uid":98139,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"太哂精神時間.放且人地咁多間分店點玩 大把野更值得做"},{"pid":"6ab719fdf62d04f8407f5ea4dacd589a8af9989b","tid":1309623,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c3368a03af364a25905497623ec4ee60b4026ef","tid":1309623,"uid":14299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"block 負皮上一頁"